      "updated": 1770287781878,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Hot Spots -> any time people want to see the post from Messi, profile pic anything request will go to Shard1. Now \nSuddenly Shard1 is out of order due to Messi is celebrity\n\nSolution ->1 Compount Shard key\n           2 Dedicatd celebrity Shard -> whenever we will see hight trafic we will move them to their shard.",
